metadata.description:
I guess I'm a killer...

written by Sara Phillips
produced by Sara Phillips, Mike Daley and Mitchell Owens.

My favorite thing about this space is the support and collaboration between artists, builders and collectors. With all of my drops, I always include a 10% donation of primary sales to various charities. With this drop, I will be personally sending this 10% BACK to the collector who mints the Golden Egg, with the hope that they use those funds to mint music NFTs from other artists in this space. 
Happy minting!!
